text: Zeke and Luther is an American sitcom. It is about two best friends trying to be the world's greatest skateboarders. It stars Hutch Dano, Adam Hicks, Daniel Curtis Lee, and Ryan Newman. The series aired from June 15, 2009 to April 2, 2012. It is set in the northern part of Gilroy, California, specifically in the fictional area of Pacific Terrace, which is stated frequently throughout the series.
